Class DatatableImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • utam.core.framework.base.UtamBaseImpl
      • utam.core.framework.base.BasePageObject
        • utam.lightning.pageobjects.impl.DatatableImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    utam.core.framework.base.PageObject, utam.core.framework.base.UtamBase, Datatable
    public final class DatatableImpl
extends utam.core.framework.base.BasePageObject
implements Datatable
    Selector: lightning-datatable Represents the lightning-datatable Lightning web component. Get cell value by index with row and column indexes, get cell value by label with in a row. Get number of rows, number of columns, check if the row with index is selectable, chek if table having rows, get count of selected rows Scroll to last row, check if row is selected, check if table is loading, check if the sortable column present in the table, click sort header button. Click select all checkbox, get width of the column by retrieving style attribute, get row header text. Check if header actions present, and row actions present. Toggle row selection. , created from JSON resources/utam/lightning/datatable.utam.json
    Version:
    1.2.0
    Author:
    Salesforce
